author: Tucker Carlson
title: Tucker Carlson: China is waging coronavirus distraction campaign
description: It’s clear how China sees the coronavirus pandemic: Not simply, or even primarily, as a public health disaster in which thousands are dying, but as part of a larger geopolitical struggle for control of the world.
